message.body: Found some ink that might be for the plotter

Ok
I don't really care about the paper though. The ink is the expensive thing.
Yeah I got that too. I think it was sent after we paid. Going to double check with the Gerber baby.

I think so but my checks already cleared and I prepaid all of it for the whole year

Hmmm.
I'll be by in a minute. Lemme take a look.
